Enum MessageType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MessageType>
Commons.MessageType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MessageType>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum MessageType
extends java.lang.Enum<MessageType>
This class defines all available message types. We provide static functions to map between tye types and the value of the enumeration.
